                <h3 id="3a">A. Why might I not like a Natural Latex mattress?</h3>
                <p>Natural Latex is a quality, healthy material for bedding, but with all of the available options, it isn’t the perfect fit for everyone. You might not like natural latex bedding if you prefer the classic  memory foam feel with its hugging sensation. Memory foam mattresses allow you to sleep more “into” the mattress, while with natural latex with its bouncy feel allows you to rest more “on top of” the mattress.</p>
